@startuml system-context
!theme plain

title Power Atlas -- System Context Diagram
caption A web application for power calculations, project management, and client requirements

skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #444444
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888

' --- Actors ---
actor "Power Engineer" as eng <<User>>
actor "Admin User" as admin <<User>>
actor "Client User" as client <<User>>

' --- Central System ---
rectangle "Power Atlas\n<<Web Application>>\n\nPower calculations, project management,\nclient requirement pipeline,\nlayout design, PDF reporting" as PA #LightBlue

' --- External Systems ---
rectangle "Email SMTP Service\n<<External Service>>\n\nSends notification emails\nfor requirements and alerts" as SMTP #LightGreen

rectangle "Moyasar Payment Gateway\n<<Future External Service>>\n\nOnline payment processing\nfor Saudi market" as PAY #LightGray

rectangle "ZATCA E-Invoicing\n<<Future External Service>>\n\nSaudi tax authority\ncompliance and e-invoicing" as ZATCA #LightGray

rectangle "IoT Sensors\n<<Future External Service>>\n\nReal-time power monitoring\nvia MQTT protocol" as IOT #LightGray

' --- Relationships: Actors to System ---
eng --> PA : "Creates projects,\nadds loads,\ngenerates reports\n[HTTPS/443]"
admin --> PA : "Manages users,\nreviews requirements,\nadministers system\n[HTTPS/443]"
client --> PA : "Submits power\nrequirements via\npublic form\n[HTTPS/443]"

' --- Relationships: System to External ---
PA --> SMTP : "Sends notification\nemails on requirement\nstatus changes\n[SMTP/587 TLS]"
PA ..> PAY : "Process payments\n[HTTPS REST API]\n<<future>>"
PA ..> ZATCA : "Submit e-invoices\n[HTTPS REST API]\n<<future>>"
IOT ..> PA : "Stream sensor\nreadings\n[MQTT/1883]\n<<future>>"

' --- Notes ---
note right of PA
  **Hosting:** Single DigitalOcean Droplet
  **OS:** Ubuntu 24.04 LTS
  **SSL:** Let's Encrypt
  **Backend:** Python Flask (port 8000)
  **Frontend:** Vite + Tailwind + vanilla JS
  **Database:** SQLite
end note

note bottom of PAY
  Dashed connections indicate
  planned future integrations
end note

@enduml
